full_summary:
**Government Tender Announcement**
=====================================================

### Tender Information

#### Title and Reference Number

* Title: Physiotherapy Services
* Reference Number: cb-5780-96103971

#### Publication and Cancellation Details

* Publication Date: 2023-05-23
* Tender Closing Date: 2023-06-08T13:00:00
* Tender Status: Expired

#### Procurement Details

* Solicitation Number: 21250-23-4242650/A
* Procurement Method: Competitive - Open Bidding
* Selection Criteria: Lowest Price

### Contract Details

* Contract Duration: 5 years from July 16, 2023 to July 15, 2028
* Contract Basis: Fixed Price

### Description of Requirement

The Correctional Service Canada (CSC) is seeking to engage a physiotherapist to provide physiotherapy services to inmates at the Nova Institution for Women in Truro, Nova Scotia. The contract period is from July 16, 2023 to July 15, 2024, with the option to renew for four (4) additional one-year periods.

The physiotherapist will be responsible for providing essential physiotherapy services, including assessments, treatment, and patient education to inmates, as well as collaborating with the institution's multidisciplinary health services team.

### Evaluation Criteria

The evaluation criteria for this tender are based on the lowest price.

### Tender Process

* Interested suppliers can download the solicitation document and associated documents from Buyandsell.gc.ca/tenders.
* Bidders can submit their bids in either English or French.
* The Crown reserves the right to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.

### Contact Information

For more information, please contact:
* Sylvie Gallant, Contracting Authority
* Telephone: 506-378-8724
* Email: Sylvie.Gallant@csc-scc.gc.ca

### Notice of Interest

Potential suppliers interested in this tender should register at Buyandsell.gc.ca/tenders and complete a supplier profile. For more information, please contact Procurement Assistance Canada.
